      <C c="0" r="46" cs="13" rs="30">
        <O><![CDATA[Autopay authorization forms are obtainable from the estate offices.
Tenants are required to bring along the completed autopay authorization
form together with their bank passbook or statement to the estate office
during office hours for the processing of their applications. Please pay
rent by other methods until the autopay amount is listed out in the bank
passbook or monthly statement.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="46" cs="13" rs="35">
        <O><![CDATA[Internet banking or phone banking account holders can pay rent through
the internet and any tone phone. You should follow the instructions of the
respective systems. Remember to choose “Hong Kong Housing
Authority” as the merchant, and enter your Electronic Payment Tenant
Code which is printed on your monthly statement to effect payment. You
are advised to keep the transaction reference code for record. Please
pay attention to the cut-off time of Respective Bank.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="47" cs="2" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="47" cs="10" rs="15">
        <O><![CDATA[Use any mobile banking apps that supports Hong Kong Housing Authority QR code bill payment to scan the FPS QR code printed on this monthly statement to make payment.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="47" cs="12" rs="11">
        <O><![CDATA[若閣下用以繳付租金之支票或所指定之自動轉帳因退回而未能成功繳付
租金，則有可能被徵收逾期利息。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="13" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[You can pay in <b><u>cash or by crossed cheque </u></b>at any estate shroff offices<br>during the rent collection service hours.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="2" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="2" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="13" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Interest may be levied when a cheque payment or a direct debit payment
is returned unpaid.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="2" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="13" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Please notify staff of the estate office or property management
companies for any change of your correspondence address.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="12" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[自動轉帳]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="12" rs="13">
        <O><![CDATA[使用支援「轉數快」二維碼繳交香港房屋委員會帳單的銀行手機應用程式，掃描此月結單上的「轉數快」二維碼進行繳費。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="12" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[可於任何屋邨繳費處的服務時間內以<b><u>現金或劃線支票</u></b>繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="12" rs="33">
        <O><![CDATA[持有銀行「網上理財」或「電話理財」戶口的租戶，可以透過互聯網和
音頻電話繳交租金。你應按個別銀行系統的指示，選擇「香港房屋委員
會」作為收款商戶，並輸入你的電子繳費租戶號碼；請保留交易編號以
作記錄。請留意個別銀行的截數時間。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="48" cs="12" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[通訊地址如有更改，請通知屋邨辦事處或商場管理公司職員。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="48" cs="11" rs="11">
        <O><![CDATA[以電話繳付 : 請撥18033，然後輸入商戶編號62，再遵照電話錄音提
示繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="48" cs="11" rs="21">
        <O><![CDATA[請以滙豐或恒生銀行發出的提款卡或具備提款功能的信用卡在滙豐或
恒生銀行的自動櫃員機繳付。請保留通知書，以便核對。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="48" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[租金/暫准證費及其他費用須在每個曆月之首日上期繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="48" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[By phone : Please call 18031, then enter Merchant Code 62, and
follow the instructions for payment.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="48" cs="11" rs="21">
        <O><![CDATA[Simply use any ATM cards or credit cards with the ATM function
issued by HSBC or Hang Seng Bank Ltd (HSB) to make your
payment at any ATM of HSBC / HSB. Please retain the customer
advice for checking.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="48" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Rent/licence fee and other charges shall be payable in advance on
the first day of every calendar month.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="49" cs="11" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[<P>可於7-Eleven以<b><u>現金</u></b>繳付。</P>]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="49" cs="11" rs="3">
        <O><![CDATA[<P>Please pay in <b><u>cash</u></b> at any 7-Eleven.</P>]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
