      <C c="0" r="130" cs="13" rs="29">
        <O><![CDATA[Autopay authorization forms are obtainable from the estate offices.
Tenants are required to bring along the completed autopay authorization
form together with their bank passbook or statement to the estate office
during office hours for the processing of their applications. Please pay
rent by other methods until the autopay amount is listed out in the bank
passbook or monthly statement.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="130" cs="13" rs="35">
        <O><![CDATA[Internet banking or phone banking account holders can pay rent through
the internet and any tone phone. You should follow the instructions of the
respective systems. Remember to choose “Hong Kong Housing
Authority” as the merchant, and enter your Electronic Payment Tenant
Code which is printed on your monthly statement to effect payment. You
are advised to keep the transaction reference code for record. Please
pay attention to the cut-off time of Respective Bank.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="131" cs="12" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[若閣下用以繳付租金之支票或所指定之自動轉帳因退回而未能成功繳付
租金，則有可能被徵收逾期利息。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="131" cs="2" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[1)]]></O>
