        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="132" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[以電話繳付 : 請撥18033，然後輸入商戶編號62，再遵照電話錄音提
示繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="132" cs="11" rs="19">
        <O><![CDATA[請以滙豐或恒生銀行發出的提款卡或具備提款功能的信用卡在滙豐或
恒生銀行的自動櫃員機繳付。請保留通知書，以便核對。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="132" cs="11" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[租金/暫准證費及其他費用須在每個曆月之首日上期繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="132" cs="11" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[By phone : Please call 18031, then enter Merchant Code 62, and
follow the instructions for payment.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="132" cs="11" rs="19">
        <O><![CDATA[Simply use any ATM cards or credit cards with the ATM function
