payment at any ATM of HSBC / HSB. Please retain the customer
advice for checking.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="132" cs="11" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[Rent/licence fee and other charges shall be payable in advance on
