      <C c="1" r="306" cs="11" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[以「繳費靈網上服務」繳付：網址為 <u>www.ppshk.com</u>。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="306" cs="11" rs="18">
        <O><![CDATA[不論業主有否正式催交，為免繳付租約/暫准證所訂的逾期利息，租
戶請於到期繳款日起計14天內清繳款項。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="306" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Through PPS by Internet at web site : <u>www.ppshk.com</u>]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="311" cs="2" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="311" cs="11" rs="28">
        <O><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 5 p.m. everyday. Payments made
after 5 p.m. will be recorded as payment made on the next
business day. Their hotlines are as follows:
7-Eleven Convenience Stores: 2299 1110.
Circle K Convenience Stores: 2991 6337.
VanGO Convenience Stores : 2586 3567.
U select : 2586 3686.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="312" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="313" cs="11" rs="8">
        <O><![CDATA[7-Eleven(只接受現金)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="313" cs="13" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[7-Eleven(Accept Cash Only)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="313" cs="11" rs="27">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款截數時間為每日下午5時正。租戶於下午5時後所交款項，將紀錄
為下一個工作天的收款。便利店/超級巿場熱線電話如下:
7-Eleven便利店 : 2299 1110。
OK便利店 : 2991 6337。
VanGO便利店 : 2586 3567。
U購select : 2586 3686。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="314" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="314" cs="2" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="314" cs="11" rs="16">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款截數時間為每日下午7時正(星期一至五)。租戶於下午7時後所交
款項，將紀錄為下一個工作天的收款。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="314" cs="11" rs="16">
        <O><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 7 p.m. (Monday to Friday). Payments
made after 7 p.m. will be recorded as payment made on the next
business day.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="317" rs="5">
