        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="317" cs="11" rs="18">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款截數時間為每日下午7時30分正(星期一至五)。租戶於下午7時30
分後所交款項，將紀錄為下一個工作天的收款。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="317" cs="11" rs="19">
        <O><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 7:30 p.m. (Monday to Friday).
Payments made after 7:30 p.m. will be recorded as payment made
on the next business day.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
