        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="378" cs="12" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[通訊地址如有更改，請通知屋邨辦事處或商場管理公司職員。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="378" cs="13" rs="9">
        <O><![CDATA[You can pay in <b><u>cash or by crossed cheque </u></b>at any estate shroff offices<br>during the rent collection service hours.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="378" cs="2" rs="5">
