        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="378" cs="13" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Please notify staff of the estate office or property management
companies for any change of your correspondence address.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="378" cs="11" rs="11">
        <O><![CDATA[以電話繳付 : 請撥18033，然後輸入商戶編號62，再遵照電話錄音提
示繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="378" cs="11" rs="21">
        <O><![CDATA[請以滙豐或恒生銀行發出的提款卡或具備提款功能的信用卡在滙豐或
恒生銀行的自動櫃員機繳付。請保留通知書，以便核對。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="378" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[租金/暫准證費及其他費用須在每個曆月之首日上期繳付。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="378" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[By phone : Please call 18031, then enter Merchant Code 62, and
follow the instructions for payment.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="378" cs="11" rs="21">
        <O><![CDATA[Simply use any ATM cards or credit cards with the ATM function
issued by HSBC or Hang Seng Bank Ltd (HSB) to make your
payment at any ATM of HSBC / HSB. Please retain the customer
advice for checking.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="378" cs="11" rs="10">
        <O><![CDATA[Rent/licence fee and other charges shall be payable in advance on
the first day of every calendar month.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="379" cs="11" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[<P>可於7-Eleven以<b><u>現金</u></b>繳付。</P>]]></O>
