      </C>
      <C c="1" r="396" cs="11" rs="17">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款截數時間為每日下午7時正(星期一至五)。租戶於下午7時後所交
款項，將紀錄為下一個工作天的收款。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="396" cs="11" rs="16">
        <O><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 7 p.m. (Monday to Friday). Payments
made after 7 p.m. will be recorded as payment made on the next
business day.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="399" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[2)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="399" cs="2" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[2)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="399" cs="11" rs="18">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款截數時間為每日下午7時30分正(星期一至五)。租戶於下午7時30
分後所交款項，將紀錄為下一個工作天的收款。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="399" cs="11" rs="19">
        <O><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 7:30 p.m. (Monday to Friday).
Payments made after 7:30 p.m. will be recorded as payment made
on the next business day.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="400" cs="13" rs="11">
        <O><![CDATA[Circle K/VanGO Convenience Stores/ U select (Accept Cash or EPS Only)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="401" cs="11" rs="8">
        <O><![CDATA[OK便利店/VanGO便利店/U購select (只接受現金或EPS)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="404" cs="2" rs="8">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="404" cs="11" rs="12">
        <O><![CDATA[Payment should not be made to any persons other than the stated
payment methods in this monthly statement.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="406" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[3)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="406" cs="11" rs="12">
        <O><![CDATA[請按此月結單上的付款方法繳交款項，切勿把款項交給其他人士。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="407" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="408" cs="11" rs="15">
        <O><![CDATA[繳款時，請出示月結單。租戶繳款後請小心核對並確保收據上的資料
無誤。並請保留收據（或按需要複印）及月結單，作為繳付紀錄，以
便核對。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="410" cs="2" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="410" cs="2" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[4)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="410" cs="11" rs="15">
        <O><![CDATA[Simply present the monthly statement when making payment.
Please check carefully and ensure details printed on the receipt
are correct. Retain the receipt or make a photocopy of it, if
required, and the monthly statement as the record of payment for
checking.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="410" cs="11" rs="7">
        <O><![CDATA[The number of daily payment per tenant code is up to 3.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="412" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[4)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="412" cs="11" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[每個租戶號碼，一天內最多只能繳交3次。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="415" cs="2" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[4)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="415" cs="11" rs="14">
        <O><![CDATA[If you have paid the rent due for payment shown in the monthly
statement or you have any enquiries on the monthly statement,
please contact our estate office or property management
companies.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="418" rs="2">
        <O><![CDATA[4)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="418" cs="11" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[如你已繳交此月結單內的到期租金，或對此月結單有任何查詢，請聯絡所屬屋邨辦事處或商場管理公司。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="422" cs="12" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[屋邨繳費處 (可接受現金或劃線支票)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="426" cs="13" rs="3">
        <O><![CDATA[Estate Shroff Office (Accept Cash or Crossed Cheque)]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="427" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="427" cs="11" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[期票／現金支票恕不接受。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="429" cs="2" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="429" cs="11" rs="3">
        <O><![CDATA[Post-dated cheques / cash cheques will not be accepted.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="430" rs="4">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="1" r="430" cs="11" rs="6">
        <O><![CDATA[劃線支票抬頭寫上「香港房屋委員會」，並於支票背頁寫上電子繳費
租戶號碼。]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="0" r="432" cs="2" rs="3">
        <O><![CDATA[●]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
      <C c="2" r="432" cs="11" rs="5">
        <O><![CDATA[Please make a crossed cheque payable to ‘Hong Kong Housing
Authority’, and write down your Electronic Payment Tenant Code
on the back of your cheque.]]></O>
        <PrivilegeControl/>
        <Expand/>
      </C>
